node.name: Tippmann Arms 25rnd Magazine
node.short_description: The Tippmann Arms 25rnd Magazine features an easy-load design and sliding outer Dust Cover. There isn’t a better rimfire magazine on the market today.
node.description:
The Tippmann Arms 25rnd Magazine features an easy-load design and sliding outer Dust Cover. There isn’t a better rimfire magazine on the market today. These magazines are built to last, stainless steel reinforced guides eliminate wear from extreme use.

Compatible only with the Tippmann Arms M4-22.

 

Tippmann Arms 25rnd Magazine Features:

25 Round Capacity
Easy Loading
Sliding Cover

node.name: Tippmann Arms Low Pro 10rnd Magazine
node.short_description: The all-new M4-22 Tippmann Arms Low Pro 10 Round Magazine is now available. Ideal for Prone and Bench Shooting.
node.description:
The all-new Tippmann Arms Low Pro 10 Round Magazine for the M4-22 rifle is now available. With its easy-load design and sliding outer Dust Cover, there isn’t a better rimfire magazine on the market today. These magazines are built to last, stainless steel reinforced guides eliminate wear from extreme use. Ideal for Prone and Bench Shooting.

 

Compatible only with the Tippmann Arms M4-22.

 

Tippmann Arms Low Pro 10rnd Magazine Features:

10 Round Capacity
Measures 4 3/8" Tall
Easy Loading
Sliding Cover
